        Changelog
        =========
        
        v1.1.0 (2017-10-14)
        -------------------
        
        - #24: Graceful fallback
        - #28: Various fix (DJ as artist, station ordering)
        
        
        v1.0.1 (2016-01-19)
        -------------------
        
        - Use httpclient helper from Mopidy >= 1.1
        
        
        v0.8.0 (2015-11-09)
        -------------------
        
        - #20: Replace HTTP with HTTPS for channels.xml
        
        
