        -------------------
        
        - #11: Add Low Bitrate encoding (aacp)
        
        
        v0.7.0 (2014-07-29)
        -------------------
        
        - #10: Remove playlists provider
        
        
        v0.6.0 (2014-03-15)
        -------------------
        
        - Directly show PLS in browser
        - Add precision about 'quality' and 'encoding' couple
        
        
        v0.5.1 (2014-03-09)
        -------------------
        
        - Fix doc typo
        
        
        v0.5.0 (2014-03-03)
