        -------------------
        
        - Require Mopidy >= 0.18
        - Add proxy support for downloading SomaFM content
        - #1: handle 'requests' exceptions
        - Use builtin Mopidy's .pls support
        - Internal code cleanup
        
        
        v0.2.0 (2013-09-22)
